      <title>印度季风降雨充沛将促进经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度预测今年的季风将高于正常水平，人们乐观地认为充足的降雨将刺激农作物产量和经济增长，并促使政府放松对小麦、大米和食糖出口的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/india-predicts-above-normal-monsoon-in-boost-to-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 09:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对俄罗斯新供应品的制裁令金属价格大幅下跌 LME</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/metals-spike-on-lme-after-russian-metal-hit-by-us-uk-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金属价格大幅波动，铝价飙升创纪录水平，随后回吐大部分涨幅，原因是交易员消化了美国和英国禁止向伦敦金属交易所交付新俄罗斯供应的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/metals-spike-on-lme-after-russian-metal-hit-by-us-uk-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:32:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
